data.description: JUST REDUCED , DON'T MISS TH3E OPPORTUNITY OF OWNING A PROPERTY CLOSE TO THE HOLLYWOOD BEACH . Beautiful single family home 2 bedrooms & 1 bathrooms,  plus 1/1 shed New wood kitchen with Granite top, stain steel appliances. Besides Bathroom completely remodeled, Property has a Gas range and Gas water Heater. All the Plumbing completely replace with PVC and some areas with copper.  Brand new Terrace done.All fenced patio that allows you to build a pool. The front has an electric gate of easy access to your driveway, plenty parking space for 5 to 6 cars . NO HAO, NO RESTRICTIONS. Close to I-95. Just 10 minutes away from the most spectacular beaches, restaurants, malls, shopping centers. Easy Showing , Do not  miss this opportunity. Plus 1/1 ( see remarks for more info )
